import React from "react"; import { Container, Row, Col, Button } from "reactstrap"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import "../styles/thank-you.css"; const ThankYou = ({ bookingDetails }) => { return (

Thank You

your tour is booked

{bookingDetails && (

Booking Details

Tour Name: {bookingDetails.tourName}
Full Name: {bookingDetails.fullName}
Phone: {bookingDetails.phone}
Guest Size: {bookingDetails.guestSize}
Booked At: {bookingDetails.bookAt}
Total Amount: ${bookingDetails.totalAmount}
)}
); }; export default ThankYou;
